data.strFullDescription:
[b]Goose, goose, DUCK?[/b] Goose, goose, DUCK? A game of social deduction where you and your fellow geese must work together to complete your mission. Keep an eye out for those malicious Mallards and other birds, who have infiltrated your team and will do anything to stop you.

[b]This Game Includes:[/b]
[list]
[*] Built-in voice chat with proximity chat option!
[*] 50+ optional sub-roles including the Dodo Bird, the Pelican, and the Morphling!
[*] 9+ maps including S.S. Mothergoose, Mallard Manor, Jungle Temple, The Basement, and Ancient Sands!
[*] 5+ built-in game modes including Classic, Draft, Trick or Treat, Dine & Dash, and Goose Hunt!
[*] Private and Public Game Lobbies.
[*] Loads of Cosmetics to customize your goose! Hats, Shirts, Farts, Pets!
[/list]

Join our community Discord to submit feedback and ideas, ask questions and find groups to play with!
[url=https://discord.gg/ggd][img]https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1568590/extras/Discord_JOINpng_copy.png?t=1685112931[/img][/url]
